Your feet need training wheels.

29
00:01:56,351 --> 00:01:59,387
Winning, losing?
Dancing is supposed to be fun.

30
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:02,190
Well, it will be fun-
if Kelly dances with me.

31
00:02:02,223 --> 00:02:05,960
Well, gee, guys, I'd love to be
partners with both of you.

32
00:02:05,994 --> 00:02:08,830
Why don't you just go
with the best dancer?

33
00:02:08,863 --> 00:02:10,865
