That's a little too bright, people.

105
00:07:18,175 --> 00:07:21,012
Where are you taking me?

106
00:07:22,046 --> 00:07:24,782
Slow down, people!
It's too fast!

107
00:07:24,815 --> 00:07:27,585
People, please!

108
00:07:27,618 --> 00:07:30,321
Surcease!

109
00:07:32,557 --> 00:07:35,593
Jessie, I'm in big trouble.

110
00:07:35,626 --> 00:07:39,197
What'd you do? Try to sell
your parents' house again?

111
00:07:39,230 --> 00:07:42,233
I can't dance.
I've been faking it for years.

112
00:07:42,266 --> 00:07:44,836
If you can't dance,
why'd you challenge Slater?

113
00:07:44,869 --> 00:07:47,739
If Kelly and Slater enter
that contest, they're going to win.

114
00:07:47,772 --> 00:07:50,475
That means their names
are going to be on the trophy.

115
00:07:50,508 --> 00:07:53,778
Together... touching.

116
00:07:53,811 --> 00:07:56,948
- So?
- So, I've got to stop them.

117
00:07:56,981 --> 00:07:59,817
I can't allow them
to "name-neck. "

118
00:07:59,851 --> 00:08:01,853
Ugh.

119
00:08:01,886 --> 00:08:04,722
Jessie, you're a terrific dancer.
Come on, you've got to help me.

120
00:08:04,756 --> 00:08:07,025
Sure I'll help.
Let's see a few of your best moves.

121
00:08:07,058 --> 00:08:09,594
Come on.

122
00:08:17,035 --> 00:08:19,037
So, what do you think?

123
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:22,073
I think you should go
with Screech.

124
00:08:27,412 --> 00:08:30,482
<i>Come in.</i>

125
00:08:31,483 --> 00:08:34,986
Mr. Belding?
My name's Casey Kasem.

126
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:42,928
I'm here to talk about
the dance party at The Max.

127
00:08:42,961 --> 00:08:46,131
"Details coming up,
right after I return. "

128
00:08:48,600 --> 00:08:51,103
Just kidding.

129
00:08:51,136 --> 00:08:53,972
Casey Kasem!
Wow.

130
00:08:54,005 --> 00:08:56,141
I heard
about the dance party.

131
