Is there anything
I can do to help?

132
00:08:58,210 --> 00:09:00,379
I'm the "Big Bopper"
around here.

133
00:09:00,412 --> 00:09:02,648
Well actually,
there is one thing.

134
00:09:02,681 --> 00:09:05,017
Well, sit down
and lay it upon me, "Big 'C."

135
00:09:06,652 --> 00:09:10,355
At "Dance Party" we try to get
the support of the local schools.

136
00:09:10,389 --> 00:09:13,592
